<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Musatake</title>
    
    <!-- Import Google Fonts: Poppins (Weights 600, 700) & Open Sans (Weights 400, 600) -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=Poppins:wght@600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        /* 1. TYPOGRAPHY SYSTEM CONFIGURATION */
        :root {
            /* Font Families */
            --font-headings: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            --font-body: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;

            /* Your Exact Type Scale */
            --font-xs: 0.75rem;    /* 12px */
            --font-sm: 0.875rem;   /* 14px */
            --font-base: 1rem;     /* 16px */
            --font-lg: 1.125rem;   /* 18px */
            --font-xl: 1.25rem;    /* 20px */
            --font-2xl: 1.5rem;    /* 24px */
            --font-3xl: 1.875rem;  /* 30px */
            --font-4xl: 2.25rem;   /* 36px */

            /* Line Heights for clean readability */
            --lh-heading: 1.3;
            --lh-body: 1.6;
        }

        /* 2. GLOBAL RESET & BASE STYLES */
        *, *::before, *::after {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: var(--font-body);
            font-size: var(--font-base);          /* Required: Body text size */
            line-height: var(--lh-body);
            color: #2d3748;
            background-color: #f7fafc;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        /* 3. APPLICATION OF TYPE SCALE TO HTML ELEMENTS */
        h1 {
            font-family: var(--font-headings);
            font-size: var(--font-4xl);          /* Required: h1 size */
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: var(--lh-heading);
            color: #1a202c;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        h2 {
            font-family: var(--font-headings);
            font-size: var(--font-3xl);          /* Required: h2 size */
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: var(--lh-heading);
            color: #2d3748;
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        }

        h3 {
            font-family: var(--font-headings);
            font-size: var(--font-2xl);          /* Required: h3 size */
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: var(--lh-heading);
            color: #4a5568;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        }

        /* Helper utility for small text element rules */
        .text-small {
            font-size: var(--font-sm);           /* Required: Small text size */
            color: #718096;
        }

        /* 4. PREVIEW CONTAINER STYLING (Just for visual layout) */
        .portfolio-preview {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .meta-caption {
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            display: block;
        }

        hr {
            border: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: #e2e8f0;
            margin: 2.5rem 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <main class="portfolio-preview">
        
        <!-- H1 Preview -->
        <span class="text-small meta-caption"></span>
        <h1>Developing Digital Solutions</h1>
        
        <p>We create digital solutions that are both functional and aesthetically pleasing, ensuring they perform well across all devices and screen sizes.</p>
        
        <hr>

        <!-- H2 Preview -->
        <span class="text-small meta-caption"></span>
        <h2>Our work speaks for itself</h2>
        <p>With customer reach across multiple markets. Our satisfaction index reflects our commitment to delivering exceptional results.</p>

        <hr>

        <!-- H3 Preview -->
        <span class="text-small meta-caption"></span>
        <h3>E-Commerce Dashboard API</h3>
        <p>A fast, responsive backend design utilizing microservices architecture. It processes requests safely and effortlessly handles variable traffic scaling spikes.</p>
        
        <!-- Small Text Preview -->
        <span class="text-small">Published on: June 26, 2026 • 4 min read</span>

    </main>

</body>
</html>
